<h2 id=3D"UC0203Rozmie=C5=88aniehotovosti-Stru=C4=8Dn=C3=BDpopis">Stru=C4=
=8Dn=C3=BD popis</h2>
<p>UC popisuje proces rozmie=C5=88ania hotovosti v aplik=C3=A1cii CashBox, =
kde pou=C5=BE=C3=ADvate=C4=BE zad=C3=A1 nomin=C3=A1ly pre Hotovos=C5=A5 IN =
a Hotovos=C5=A5 OUT, syst=C3=A9m priebe=C5=BEne prepo=C4=8D=C3=ADtava rozdi=
el a n=C3=A1sledne zobraz=C3=AD s=C3=BAhrn oper=C3=A1cie. V z=C3=A1vislosti=
 od variantu sa poplatok rie=C5=A1i bu=C4=8F hotovos=C5=A5ou (poplatkov=C3=
=A1 mincovka) alebo strhnut=C3=ADm z =C3=BA=C4=8Dtu</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class=3D"columnLayout single" data-layout=3D"single">
<div class=3D"cell normal" data-type=3D"normal">
<div class=3D"innerCell">
<h2 style=3D"text-align: left;" id=3D"UC0203Rozmie=C5=88aniehotovosti-=C3=
=9A=C4=8Del">=C3=9A=C4=8Del</h2>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(31,31,31);">Postup pre vykonanie oper=C3=A1cie=
 rozmie=C5=88ania hotovosti v pokladni=C4=8Dnom procese tak, aby bolo mo=C5=
=BEn=C3=A9 oper=C3=A1ciu jednoducho zada=C5=A5, skontrolova=C5=A5 a evidova=
=C5=A5 v syst=C3=A9me vr=C3=A1tane uplatnenia poplatku (a pr=C3=ADpadnej z=
=C4=BEavy) pod=C4=BEa typu klienta a zvolen=C3=A9ho sp=C3=B4sobu =C3=BAhrad=
y poplatku</span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class=3D"columnLayout single" data-layout=3D"single">
<div class=3D"cell normal" data-type=3D"normal">
<div class=3D"innerCell">
