lor: rgb(0,0,0);">Hlavn=C3=BD tok</span></h2>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"><s=
pan style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);"><span>&nbsp;</span></span><strong>Rozmi=
enanie hotovosti (fyzick=C3=A1 osoba s poplatkom z GATE prekliku)</strong><=
/span></span></p>
<ol>
<li><p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);"><span class=3D"inline-comment-=
marker" data-ref=3D"19b8dde7-9f03-4c4f-bfd1-0382c90dae02">Syst=C3=A9m zavol=
=C3=A1</span></span><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);"><span class=3D"in=
