ol=C3=AD </span><strong>Pokra=C4=8Dova=C5=A5</strong></p></li>
<li><p>Syst=C3=A9m<span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">&nbsp;zobraz=C3=AD for=
mul=C3=A1r pre&nbsp;</span>poplatok (mincovka)<span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0=
,0);">&nbsp;s =C4=8Das=C5=A5ami<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span><strong>Hotovo=
