 priebe=C5=BEne zobrazuje&nbsp;</span><strong>Difference</strong><span styl=
e=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">&nbsp;pod=C4=BEa zadan=C3=BDch nomin=C3=A1lov</spa=
n></p></li>
<li>Spust=C3=AD sa&nbsp;<a href=3D"https://confluenceit.tatrabanka.sk/confl=
uence/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=3D215857272#:~:text=3DAnalytics-,UC0405%=
20%2D%20Pr%C3%ADprava%20%2D%20Mincovka,-Created%20by%20Mat%C3%BA%C5%A1" rel=
