<li style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">Pou=C5=
=BE=C3=ADvate=C4=BE&nbsp;zvol=C3=AD tla=C4=8Didlo <strong>Pokra=C4=8Dova=C5=
=A5</strong></span></li>
<li style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">Syst=C3=A9m<span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0=
);">&nbsp;zobraz=C3=AD&nbsp;</span><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102);"><a=
 href=3D"https://confluenceit.tatrabanka.sk/confluence/pages/viewpage.actio=
