latkom</span> vr=C3=A1tane po=C4=BEa </span><strong>Popis</strong></li>
<li><p>Pou=C5=BE=C3=ADvate=C4=BE<span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"> vypln=
=C3=AD </span><strong>Popis</strong> <span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">a z=
vol=C3=AD </span><strong>Potvrdi=C5=A5</strong></p></li>
<li><p><span style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">Syst=C3=A9m:</span></p>
<ul>
<li style=3D"list-style-type: none;">
<ul>
<li>zavol=C3=A1 winward a vygeneruje dokument=C3=A1ciu pre vklad pod=C4=BEa=
<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=3D"https://confluenceit.tatrabanka.sk/confluence=
/display/DOKIT/Klientske+dokumenty" rel=3D"nofollow">Klientske dokumenty - =
AppLib - ConfluenceIT</a>&nbsp;a zalo=C5=BE=C3=AD podpisovac=C3=AD proces v=
 DSA aplik=C3=A1cii</li>
<li>presmeruje pracovn=C3=ADka TB z okna aplik=C3=A1cie do aplik=C3=A1cie D=
SA a otvor=C3=AD vytvoren=C3=BD podpisovac=C3=AD proces</li>
<li>Klient TB s Pracovn=C3=ADk TB vykonaj=C3=BA podpisovanie dokumentov v a=
plik=C3=A1cii DSA</li>
</ul></li>
</ul></li>
<li style=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102);">S=
yst=C3=A9m obdr=C5=BE=C3=AD inform=C3=A1ciu z aplik=C3=A1cie DSA o korektno=
m dokon=C4=8Den=C3=AD podpisovania</span>
<ul>
<li>zobraz=C3=AD hl=C3=A1senie typu info :<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=3D"htt=
ps://confluenceit.tatrabanka.sk/confluence/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=3D2=
01603793" rel=3D"nofollow" style=3D"">I024</a> a&nbsp;<a href=3D"https://co=
nfluenceit.tatrabanka.sk/confluence/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=3D20160379=
3#:~:text=3Dproces%20%C3%BAspe%C5%A1ne%20ukon%C4%8Den%C3%BD-,I025,-%2D%20Pr=
os%C3%ADm%20nezabudnite%20vzia%C5%A5" rel=3D"nofollow">I025 </a></li>
</ul></li>
<li style=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102);">P=
ou=C5=BE=C3=ADvate=C4=BE po =C3=BAspe=C5=A1nej kontrole zvol=C3=AD mo=C5=BE=
nos=C5=A5 <strong>Ulo=C5=BEi=C5=A5</strong> <strong>a uzavrie=C5=A5</strong=
></span></li>
<li style=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102);">K=
oniec UC</span></li>
</ol>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">=
<strong>Rozmienanie hotovosti (fyzick=C3=A1 osoba v mene pr=C3=A1vnickej os=
oby, ktor=C3=A1 nema zv=C3=BDhodnenie)</strong></span></span></p>
<ol>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">Popis tohto HT je zhodn=C3=BD ako HT=
 - <a href=3D"https://confluenceit.tatrabanka.sk/confluence/pages/viewpage.=
action?pageId=3D234578400#:~:text=3D%C2%A0Rozmienanie%20hotovosti%20(fyzick=
%C3%A1%20osoba)" rel=3D"nofollow">Rozmienanie hotovosti (fyzick=C3=A1 osoba=
)</a></span></li>
<li>Rozdiel je iba v:</li>
<ol>
<li>Syst=C3=A9m dotiahne do obrazovky okrem fyzickej osobe inform=C3=A1cie =
aj firemn=C3=A9 =C3=BAdaje (spolo=C4=8Dnos=C5=A5, Adresa, I=C4=8CO a at=C4=
=8F) a zobraz=C3=AD ich v s=C3=BAhrne</li>
<li>Syst=C3=A9m nastav=C3=AD re=C5=BEim bez z=C4=BEavy&nbsp;</li>
<li>Poplatok sa rie=C5=A1i v hotovosti cez poplatkov=C3=BA mincovku (kroky =
5=E2=80=937)</li>
</ol>
</ol>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">=
<strong><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,=
0);">Rozmienanie hotovosti (fyzick=C3=A1 osoba v mene pr=C3=A1vnickej osoby=
, ktor=C3=A1 m=C3=A1 zv=C3=BDhodnenie) - poplatok sa =C3=BA=C4=8Dtuje z =C3=
=BA=C4=8Dtu</span></span></strong></span></span></p>
<ol>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"=
><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">Po=
pis tohto HT je zhodn=C3=BD ako HT - <a href=3D"https://confluenceit.tatrab=
anka.sk/confluence/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=3D234578400#:~:text=3DRozmi=
enanie%20hotovosti%20(fyzick%C3%A1%20osoba)" rel=3D"nofollow">Rozmienanie h=
otovosti (fyzick=C3=A1 osoba)</a></span></span></span></span></li>
<li>Rozdiel je iba v:</li>
<ol>
<li>Do s=C3=BAhrnej obrazovky sa dotiahnu =C3=BAdaje poplatok + z=C4=BEava =
+ inform=C3=A1ciu, =C5=BEe poplatok bude strhnut=C3=BD z konkr=C3=A9tneho =
=C3=BA=C4=8Dtu</li>
<li>Neobjav=C3=AD sa hotovostn=C3=A1 poplatkov=C3=A1 mincovka (lebo sa nest=
rh=C3=A1va cash)</li>
<li>Koniec transakcie je bez vyber hotovos=C5=A5, resp. poplatok sa za=C3=
=BA=C4=8Dtuje po potvrden=C3=AD</li>
</ol>
</ol>
<p><br></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
