<div class=3D"columnLayout single" data-layout=3D"single">
<div class=3D"cell normal" data-type=3D"normal">
<div class=3D"innerCell">
<h2 id=3D"UC0203Rozmie=C5=88aniehotovosti-V=C3=BDsledok">V=C3=BDsledok</h2>
<p>V=C3=BDsledkom UC je, =C5=BEe rozmie=C5=88anie hotovosti je v CashBoxe k=
orektne ulo=C5=BEen=C3=A1 a zaevidovan=C3=A1 so v=C5=A1etk=C3=BDmi zadan=C3=
=BDmi nomin=C3=A1lmi (Hotovos=C5=A5 IN/OUT), vypo=C4=8D=C3=ADtan=C3=BDmi su=
mami a rozdielom, s uveden=C3=BDm poplatkom (vr=C3=A1tane sp=C3=B4sobu =C3=
=BAhrady a pr=C3=ADpadnej z=C4=BEavy)</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class=3D"columnLayout single" data-layout=3D"single">
<div class=3D"cell normal" data-type=3D"normal">
<div class=3D"innerCell">
<h1 id=3D"UC0203Rozmie=C5=88aniehotovosti-Grafick=C3=A9pou=C5=BE=C3=ADvate=
=C4=BEsk=C3=A9rozhranie">Grafick=C3=A9 pou=C5=BE=C3=ADvate=C4=BEsk=C3=A9 ro=
zhranie</h1>
<p><br></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>S=C3=BAhrnn=C3=A1 obrazovka Rozmie=C5=88anie hotovosti (s poplat=
kom / bez poplatku )obsahuje:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><p><strong>=C4=8Ciastka [EUR]</strong> =E2=80=93 zobrazen=C3=A1 hodnota=
&nbsp;</p></li>
<li><p><strong>Po=C4=8Det nomin=C3=A1li=C3=AD</strong> =E2=80=93 zobrazen=
=C3=A1 hodnota&nbsp;</p></li>
<li><p><strong>Poplatok [EUR]</strong> + inform=C3=A1cia&nbsp;=E2=80=93 zob=
razen=C3=A9 hodnoty&nbsp;</p></li>
<li><p><strong>Z=C4=BEava %</strong> =E2=80=93 zobrazen=C3=A1 hodnota&nbsp;=
</p></li>
<li><p><strong>Popis</strong>&nbsp;=E2=80=93<span>&nbsp;</span><strong>edit=
ovate=C4=BEn=C3=A9</strong>&nbsp;</p></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
